    <title>日本阴间奥运会骚操作！奥林匹克精神没见到，抗日精神倒是给我唤醒了！</title>
    <link href="https://www.iflu.cf/2021/07/29/rubbish-Japan-olympics-no-olympics-spirit-but-have-anti-Japanese-spirit/"/>
    <id>https://www.iflu.cf/2021/07/29/rubbish-Japan-olympics-no-olympics-spirit-but-have-anti-Japanese-spirit/</id>
    <published>2021-07-29T14:36:15.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-08-13T01:01:50.999Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>这几天大家</p><p>都没少气死在阴间奥运会上吧</p><p>u1s1</p><p>看了几天的奥运会</p><p>奥林匹克精神没见到</p><p>抗日精神倒是给我唤醒了</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729223103.png" alt="图片"></p><p>你们感受下本次阴间奥运会集锦</p><p>见识下日本人的脸皮有多厚</p><p><strong>1</strong></p><p><strong>女子水球小组中</strong></p><p><strong>日本选手直接压在中国选手身上游</strong></p><p>连正主都气到直接下场明涵</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729223058.webp" alt="图片"></p><p>你们感受下</p><p>喵差点以为这是在谋杀</p><p>压着中国选手游</p><p>用头使劲儿撞中国选手</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729223116.gif" alt="图片"></p><p><strong>2</strong></p><p>体操男子个人全能决赛中</p><p>中国选手和日本选手桥本大辉</p><p>迷惑分数对比</p><p>14.9 VS 14.7</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729223128.gif" alt="图片"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729223042.gif" alt="图片"></p><p>就是这样一脚出界的桥本大辉</p><p>还夺得了金牌，而我们得了银牌</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729223001.webp" alt="图片"></p><p><strong>3</strong></p><p>乒乓球混双比赛中</p><p><strong>日本选手水谷隼吹球犯规</strong></p><p><strong>伊藤美诚球台犯规</strong></p><p>裁判选择看不见给了金牌</p><p>不止一次手摸桌+吹球</p><p>（还特么是为了防中国定出的阴间规矩，结果自己犯规了）</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729223023.gif" alt="图片"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222950.webp" alt="图片"></p><p>4</p><p><strong>东京奥运村的环境差到什么程度？</strong></p><p>连日本自己都不愿意住</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222947.webp" alt="图片"></p><p>这tm是东京奥运会吗？</p><p>是阴间奥运会吧</p><p>差点没被恶心死了</p><p>能理解东道主对金牌有追求是正常的</p><p>但这吃相未免也太难看了吧？</p><p>就差把金牌直接挂脖子上了…</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222945.gif" alt="图片"></p><p>而今天<strong>孙颖莎VS伊藤美诚</strong>的</p><p>乒乓球女单比赛</p><p>真真是为我们争了口气</p><p>大魔王都莎疯了！！</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222941.png" alt="图片"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222939.png" alt="图片"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222937.webp" alt="图片"></p><p><strong>4-0压倒性的胜利</strong></p><p>比赛全程看得热血沸腾</p><p>网友评论也给喵笑晕了</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222935.webp" alt="图片"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222932.webp" alt="图片"></p><p>中国乒乓球队痛失铜牌</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222930.webp" alt="图片"></p><p>还有先前曝出</p><p>伊藤美城的妈妈从小就对伊藤说：</p><p>能战胜中国的人只有你</p><p><strong>网友：你妈都是骗你的</strong></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222926.png" alt="图片"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222923.webp" alt="图片"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222921.png" alt="图片"></p><p>记者：怎么看待今晚伊藤的决赛</p><p>陈梦：等她进了再说吧</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222918.webp" alt="图片"></p><p>笋都被网友夺完了</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222914.png" alt="图片"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222911.webp" alt="图片"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222909.webp" alt="图片"></p><p>真的被网友的吐槽笑不活了</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222907.png" alt="图片"></p><p>讲真的，</p><p>在看东京奥运会之前</p><p>喵一直觉得自己是理智爱国</p><p>但是这几天的观看比赛全程下来</p><p>喵嘴巴优美中国话就没有停过</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222902.png" alt="图片"></p><p>几句话真的无法表达喵的情绪</p><p>整合了下网友们的精辟吐槽</p><p>任君选择</p><p>总有一款是你口味</p><p>▼</p><p>咋不直接把奖牌都给日本队</p><p>整这仪式干嘛呢</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222859.webp" alt="图片"></p><p>重新定义了什么是东道主</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222857.webp" alt="图片"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729223157.png" alt="图片"></p><p>让我们每天都在刷新知识点</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222849.png" alt="图片"></p><p>很难不为眼瞎裁判坚持比赛而动容</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222846.webp" alt="图片"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222844.png" alt="图片"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222841.png" alt="图片"></p><p>打开微博</p><p>随时随地，发现日本作弊</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222836.webp" alt="图片"></p><p>桥本的金牌</p><p>表面上：自己努力的成果</p><p>实际上：裁判努力的成果</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222834.webp" alt="图片"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222832.webp" alt="图片"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/aniamOSdT9tKibjIBZkibhN88f7YZjQKib9ic7tHVHrbCSRia1ROibKoumo2IyBiaemGCUtp1Pra8jpKV1EIvickfgxGDvw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222830.webp" alt="图片"></p><p>昨晚的朋友圈</p><p>都成了义愤填膺现场</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222827.webp" alt="图片"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222821.webp" alt="图片"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222817.webp" alt="图片"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/aniamOSdT9tKibjIBZkibhN88f7YZjQKib9icQjwicgXWUGW24YibzPPfWsoJyDZk1ok7UJfGg6GiaHSIdkYQPK7dEbBBg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222814.webp" alt="图片"></p><p>不仅中国网友强烈不满</p><p>毕竟观众都是长了眼睛的</p><p>东京奥运会裁判的行为引起公愤</p><p>在外网也是骂声连连</p><p>这绝壁是历史上最垃圾的一次奥运会</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222807.webp" alt="图片"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222803.webp" alt="图片"></p><p>所以，</p><p>不让观众入场说是为了防疫</p><p>其实也是害怕运动员和裁判被揍吧</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222759.webp" alt="图片"></p><p>小时候不明白</p><p>为什么大人们都讨厌日本</p><p>觉得他们带有偏见</p><p>现在明白了:</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222756.webp" alt="图片"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222731.webp" alt="图片"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222735.webp" alt="图片"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222738.gif" alt="图片"></p><p>尽管知道东京奥运会阴招很多，</p><p>可以说是拼尽全力阻止中国赢奥运会：</p><p>改工具，改规则，改场地，</p><p>裁判眼瞎 …</p><p><strong>但是没有人能阻挡中国队得第一</strong></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222723.webp" alt="图片"></p><p>孙颖莎4-0大胜伊藤美诚</p><p><strong>国乒女单提前包揽冠亚军</strong></p><p><strong><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222720.webp" alt="图片"></strong></p><p>张雨霏游泳比赛打破奥运会纪录</p><p><strong>夺得第十三金</strong></p><p>**<br>**</p><p><em><strong>*<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222717.webp" alt="图片">*</strong></em></p><p><em><strong>*<br>*</strong></em></p><p>女子4乘200米自由泳决赛打破世界纪录</p><p><strong>夺得第十四金</strong></p><p>**<br>**</p><p><strong><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222710.webp" alt="图片"></strong></p><p>…….</p><p>奖牌还在不断增加</p><p>中国的运动员在用行动告诉世界</p><p>什么才是真正的实力</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222707.webp" alt="图片"></p><p>确实，从小到大我们接受的教育</p><p>是让我们学会公平公正</p><p>要多角度大格局</p><p>但是通过这次东京奥运会的</p><p>一系列阴间操作</p><p>让我重新认识到了</p><p>这等卑劣蛮荒的小国</p><p>真的不配</p><p>和我们5千年的泱泱大国相提并论</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222701.webp" alt="图片"></p><p>就像觉醒时代里辜鸿铭说的一段关于</p><p><strong>中国人和日本人的礼仪区别：</strong></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222659.webp" alt="图片"></p><p>中国人的礼貌是发自内心的</p><p>而日本人的礼貌是排列式的礼貌</p><p>繁杂而令人不快</p><p>不是发自内心，出于自然的礼貌</p><p>是一种没有芬芳的花儿</p><p>形容的太贴切了</p><p>最后用一段</p><p>我们奥运健儿们赛场上的动图</p><p>来结束这篇文章吧</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222653.gif" alt="图片"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222633.gif" alt="图片"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222637.gif" alt="图片"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222621.gif" alt="图片"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729222614.gif" alt="图片"></p><blockquote><p>本文转载自<a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU1ODY0NTc3Mg==&mid=2247484860&idx=1&sn=aa18e1a5d8c3117e3ee354de5d143b67&chksm=fc2212dfcb559bc94ff6045ed8bb3c1337df892dd4c840f86d7282b85b3f9711a682198d7e38&xtrack=1&scene=90&subscene=93&sessionid=1627566883&clicktime=1627566884&enterid=1627566884&ascene=56&devicetype=android-30&version=28000753&nettype=WIFI&abtest_cookie=AAACAA==&lang=zh_CN&exportkey=A0x5NW+trO9Du/iiMtYq/co=&pass_ticket=bSm0A4O+RFCPWCbEXXVQ3xjWjVQNTu3+/W+gL7Lj63OVuhnm/ooDos7RpbljyHh0&wx_header=1">“日本阴间奥运会骚操作！” 奥林匹克精神没见到，抗日精神倒是给我唤醒了！</a></p><p>若有侵权，请联系站长删除</p></blockquote>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
