    <title>Ubuntu搭建我的世界基岩版</title>
    <link href="https://www.iflu.cf/2021/07/05/Ubuntu-create-Minecraft-Bedrock-Edition/"/>
    <id>https://www.iflu.cf/2021/07/05/Ubuntu-create-Minecraft-Bedrock-Edition/</id>
    <published>2021-07-05T11:14:22.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-08-13T01:01:58.389Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>前言：群里一个大憨憨在搭建我的世界基岩版，一堆错误。所以让他扔给我机子搭建。</p></blockquote><h3 id="1、安装必要工具"><a href="#1、安装必要工具" class="headerlink" title="1、安装必要工具"></a>1、安装必要工具</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo -i</span><br><span class="line">apt-get install wget screen bash</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2、安装"><a href="#2、安装" class="headerlink" title="2、安装"></a>2、安装</h3><h4 id="1-创建目录-进入目录（可省略）"><a href="#1-创建目录-进入目录（可省略）" class="headerlink" title="1.创建目录 进入目录（可省略）"></a>1.创建目录 进入目录（可省略）</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkdir /mc</span><br><span class="line">cd /mc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="2-服务端下载解压安装"><a href="#2-服务端下载解压安装" class="headerlink" title="2.服务端下载解压安装"></a>2.服务端下载解压安装</h4><p>此处使用的是1.17.2.01版本，可自行去<a href="https://www.minecraft.net/en-us/download/server/bedrock">Bedrock Server Download | Minecraft</a>获取最新版本</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget https://minecraft.azureedge.net/bin-linux/bedrock-server-1.17.2.01.zip  #下载</span><br><span class="line">unzip bedrock-server-1.17.2.01.zip  #解压</span><br><span class="line">apt install -y libcurl4-openssl-dev  #安装libcurl4-openssl-dev</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="3-运行"><a href="#3-运行" class="headerlink" title="3.运行"></a>3.运行</h4><p>先给/mc目录777权限</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">chmod -R 777 /mc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>建议先screen一下，这样子可直接断开连接服务也在运行</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">screen -S mc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后再运行</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">LD_LIBRARY_PATH=. ./bedrock_server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>显示</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/DaoChen6/img@main/img/20210729230739.png" alt="image-20210705192319353"></p><p>成功运行，可愉快玩耍。</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;前言：群里一个大憨憨在搭建我的世界基岩版，一堆错误。所以让他扔给我机子搭建。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
